Welcome to Vinea

Rooted in community. Inspired by the vine.

On beautiful Daniel Island, where the breeze drifts through the live oaks and the evening light lingers, Vinea invites you to slow down, savor, and connect. Relax with European-inspired dishes, delightful wines, and genuine hospitality!
More About Us 
Hours

Tuesday – Thursday | 5PM – 9PMFriday – Saturday | 5PM – 9PM

Our Menu
Fresh flavors. Inspired by Europe. 
Fresh, approachable dishes inspired by European flavors — made with passion and served with warmth.

Tomato Mozzarella Tower

Grilled Salmon

Braised Short Rib

Homemade Desserts

Cavatelli Amatriciana

Grilled Octopus

Discover entire menu

Come See Us!

On beautiful Daniel Island, where live oaks meet the water’s edge — discover an inviting dining experience just steps from the marina.
